00:26:19.030 --> 00:26:23.140 align:middle line:84%
A horse, a cat, a dolphin, a dog
will know exactly how you feel,

00:26:23.140 --> 00:26:26.620 align:middle line:84%
regardless how different
they are as a species.

00:26:26.620 --> 00:26:32.080 align:middle line:84%
Energy is a universal
language that all animals

00:26:32.080 --> 00:26:36.370 align:middle line:84%
have the capability
to be mindfully aware.

00:26:36.370 --> 00:26:38.950 align:middle line:84%
>> If one has a spiritual
radiance about him,

00:26:38.950 --> 00:26:40.420 align:middle line:90%
you sense it.

00:26:40.420 --> 00:26:41.470 align:middle line:90%
You sense in the eyes.

