the spirits of the people

00:26:45.800 --> 00:26:46.600 align:middle line:90%
around him.

00:26:46.600 --> 00:26:49.600 align:middle line:84%
That's what's remarkable
all over the world,

00:26:49.600 --> 00:26:50.811 align:middle line:90%
everywhere I've gone.

