You practice mindful breathing.

00:27:50.310 --> 00:27:54.080 align:middle line:84%
You generate the
energy of mindfulness,

00:27:54.080 --> 00:27:56.720 align:middle line:84%
and with that energy
of mindfulness,

00:27:56.720 --> 00:28:00.230 align:middle line:84%
