anger is in you.

00:28:00.230 --> 00:28:03.780 align:middle line:84%
Breathing in, I
know anger is in me.

00:28:03.780 --> 00:28:06.930 align:middle line:84%
Breathing out, I'm taking
good care of my anger.

00:28:06.930 --> 00:28:10.370 align:middle line:90%
I'm holding it peacefully.

00:28:10.370 --> 00:28:13.370 align:middle line:84%
And the energy of mindfulness
embracing the energy

00:28:13.370 --> 00:28:17.180 align:middle line:84%
of anger, although energy
of anger is still there,

00:28:17.180 --> 00:28:21.260 align:middle line:84%
