mindfulness is also there.

00:28:21.260 --> 00:28:23.330 align:middle line:84%
Mindfulness tell
you that anger--

00:28:23.330 --> 00:28:27.890 align:middle line:84%
while you are anger, is not goo
say anything, to do anything.

00:28:27.890 --> 00:28:31.080 align:middle line:90%
It may cause damage.

00:28:31.080 --> 00:28:33.110 align:middle line:84%
So do you just
continue to practice

00:28:33.110 --> 00:28:35.990 align:middle line:84%
mindful breathing,
mindful walking,

00:28:35.990 --> 00:28:38.510 align:middle line:84%
so that you can take
care of your anger.

00:28:38.510 --> 00:28:45.000 align:middle line:84%
And you get a relief, and if you
practice looking more deeply,

00:28:45.000 --> 00:28:48.020 align:middle line:84%
