00:28:55.400 --> 00:28:57.380 align:middle line:90%
in the other person.

00:28:57.380 --> 00:28:59.690 align:middle line:84%
And if you recognize
things like that,

00:28:59.690 --> 00:29:04.390 align:middle line:90%
you can transform your anger.

00:29:04.390 --> 00:29:10.940 align:middle line:84%
Sometime, many times,
the seat of anger in you

00:29:10.940 --> 00:29:14.200 align:middle line:90%
is very important.

00:29:14.200 --> 00:29:16.220 align:middle line:84%
Other people, when they
hear the same sentence,

00:29:16.220 --> 00:29:17.320 align:middle line:90%
they don't get angry.

00:29:17.320 --> 00:29:20.840 align:middle line:84%
But you, you get angry because
of the seat of anger in you

