comes from you more than

00:29:28.310 --> 00:29:29.930 align:middle line:90%
from the other person.

00:29:29.930 --> 00:29:34.940 align:middle line:84%
So that is the kind of insight
that can help you to transform.

00:29:34.940 --> 00:29:39.410 align:middle line:84%
And then when you look
deeply at the other person,

00:29:39.410 --> 00:29:43.970 align:middle line:84%
