see that it is possible for us

00:53:25.580 --> 00:53:29.250 align:middle line:84%
to go through these things
peacefully, sickness,

00:53:29.250 --> 00:53:32.630 align:middle line:90%
old age, and death.

00:53:32.630 --> 00:53:38.960 align:middle line:84%
When you look at a cloud
