00:53:38.960 --> 00:53:41.510 align:middle line:84%
you'll see that the
nature of a cloud

00:53:41.510 --> 00:53:44.615 align:middle line:84%
is a nature of no
birth and no death.

00:53:44.615 --> 00:53:50.150 align:middle line:84%
A cloud has not
come from non-being

00:53:50.150 --> 00:53:53.510 align:middle line:90%
before the cloud is a cloud.

00:53:53.510 --> 00:53:57.770 align:middle line:84%
The cloud had been
other things, so a cloud

00:53:57.770 --> 00:54:00.500 align:middle line:90%
has not come from nothing.

00:54:00.500 --> 00:54:04.360 align:middle line:84%
So the nature of the
cloud is no birth.

00:54:04.360 --> 00:54:07.850 align:middle line:84%
The appearance of the
cloud, the form of a cloud

00:54:07.850 --> 00:54:09.830 align:middle line:90%
is only a continuation.

00:54:09.830 --> 00:54:14.210 align:middle line:84%
Before the cloud is a cloud,
it has been the water vapor.

00:54:14.210 --> 00:54:16.740 align:middle line:84%
It has been the
water in the ocean,

00:54:16.740 --> 00:54:20.000 align:middle line:90%
the heat generated by the sun.

00:54:20.000 --> 00:54:26.870 align:middle line:84%
So the cloud is
only a continuation.

00:54:26.870 --> 00:54:32.720 align:middle line:84%
And when the cloud cease to
be a cloud, that's not dying.

00:54:32.720 --> 00:54:35.030 align:middle line:90%
A cloud cannot die.

00:54:35.030 --> 00:54:37.726 align:middle line:84%
It's impossible
for a cloud to die.

00:54:37.726 --> 00:54:43.040 align:middle line:84%
A cloud can become
rain, snow, or ice,

00:54:43.040 --> 00:54:46.430 align:middle line:84%
but a cloud cannot
become nothing.

00:54:46.430 --> 00:54:50.840 align:middle line:84%
And if the cloud
knows how to meditate,

00:54:50.840 --> 00:54:57.620 align:middle line:84%
it will see that this nature is
nature of no death, no drying.

00:54:57.620 --> 00:55:00.160 align:middle line:84%
To be a cloud floating
in the sky is wonderful,

00:55:00.160 --> 00:55:03.230 align:middle line:84%
but to become the rain falling
on a rice field on a mountain

00:55:03.230 --> 00:55:04.880 align:middle line:90%
is also wonderful.

00:55:04.880 --> 00:55:07.400 align:middle line:90%


00:55:07.400 --> 00:55:10.280 align:middle line:84%
And a cloud can look down
and see part of the cloud

00:55:10.280 --> 00:55:17.420 align:middle line:84%
has become the river, so to
become a river is so nice.

00:55:17.420 --> 00:55:20.660 align:middle line:84%
And when you practice
meditation deeply,

00:55:20.660 --> 00:55:22.910 align:middle line:84%
you see that your
nature is nature

00:55:22.910 --> 00:55:24.800 align:middle line:84%
of no birth and
no death, and you

00:55:24.800 --> 00:55:29.963 align:middle line:84%
can transcend the fear of
birth and death, you see?

00:55:29.963 --> 00:55:31.380 align:middle line:84%
So there are many
ways of practice

00:55:31.380 --> 00:55:35.120 align:middle line:90%
in order to deal with our fear.

00:55:35.120 --> 00:55:39.230 align:middle line:84%
And because we are so
busy now in daily life,

00:55:39.230 --> 00:55:42.390 align:middle line:84%
we have no time in
our life to practice.

00:55:42.390 --> 00:55:47.360 align:middle line:84%
We have become victims of our
fear and anger, frustration.

00:55:47.360 --> 00:55:49.160 align:middle line:84%
And that is why
is very important

00:55:49.160 --> 00:55:55.610 align:middle line:84%
that everyone in society should
bring in a spiritual dimension

00:55:55.610 --> 00:55:58.370 align:middle line:84%
to their life, so that
they will suffer less.

00:55:58.370 --> 00:56:03.560 align:middle line:84%
A politician, a businessman,
a schoolteacher, a filmmaker

00:56:03.560 --> 00:56:09.230 align:middle line:84%
